  "detailed_description": "<strong>Percussive VR</strong> is a collection of virtual instruments you can play in your home! Learn, practice, perform, or just play — your own creativity is the limit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Instruments</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Marimba<br></li><li> Xylophone<br></li><li> Vibraphone<br></li><li> Steelpan / Steel Drums<br></li><li> Glockenspiel<br></li><li> <i>More to come!</i></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Sheet music import<br></li><li> Customizable metronome<br></li><li> Optional note names/labels<br></li><li> Different mallets (for different types of sound)<br></li><li> Adjustable instrument heights<br></li><li> <i>More to come!</i></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Percussive VR</strong> is a collection of virtual instruments you can play in your home! Learn, practice, perform, or just play — your own creativity is the limit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Instruments</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Marimba<br></li><li> Xylophone<br></li><li> Vibraphone<br></li><li> Steelpan / Steel Drums<br></li><li> Glockenspiel<br></li><li> <i>More to come!</i></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Sheet music import<br></li><li> Customizable metronome<br></li><li> Optional note names/labels<br></li><li> Different mallets (for different types of sound)<br></li><li> Adjustable instrument heights<br></li><li> <i>More to come!</i></li></ul>",
